  <h2>🚀 What is Maker?</h2>
  <p><strong>Maker</strong> is a dead simple CLI tool for scaffolding new projects. Whether it's a website, app, or backend tool, Maker gets you started instantly.</p>

  <h2>📦 Install</h2>
  <CodeBlock code="npm install -g gomaker" />

  <h2>⚡ Usage</h2>
  <CodeBlock code="maker" />

  <h2>✨ Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Instant folder setup</li>
    <li>Support for multiple frameworks</li>
    <li>Zero config required</li>
  </ul>

  <a class="button" href="https://github.com/xamyl/maker" target="_blank">View on GitHub</a>
</Layout>
